liberal media types,

00:38.739 --> 00:40.273
especially in New York City
and Hollywood,

00:40.306 --> 00:42.909
hate the US military,
hate the president,

00:42.943 --> 00:45.178
and, frankly,
hate me and guys like me.

00:45.211 --> 00:46.813
Look what
they've done to Rush.

00:46.847 --> 00:48.314
MAN (over TV): Nobody hates
the US military, I'm just...

00:48.348 --> 00:50.150
MAN (over TV): Bottom line
is liberals in this country

00:50.183 --> 00:53.620
want to pursue their big
government socialist policies,

00:53.654 --> 00:55.388
they hate any free enterprise,
they hate capitalism,

00:55.421 --> 00:57.858
and they hate...

